songs.title: ​crawl
songs.lyrics:
[Lyrics from Snippet]

...it's never-ending
This happens every time
I swear I never meant this
I needed love, I needed love
’Cause I don't love me
And is it too late?
Yeah, is it all too late?

I crawl
I walk
I run
I fall
You needed me
So bite your tongue
But I can't see past my pain
I caved in but you won’t still take me back
I know you care, I know you care
I know you wanted this more than me
I know you're torn, I know you're torn
So can I take it back
You know I would
You know I'd take it all

I swear it's always been you
Taste it on your neck now
Feel it in your chest
Yeah, yeah
So tell me are we nothing?
Baby, tell me something
Yeah, yeah

I know you care, I know you care
I know you wanted this more than me
I know you're torn, I know you're torn
So can I take you back?
You know I would
